 \"POM dependencies for Typesafe Config, log4j, log4j2, and slf4j are optional integrations, not required setup for core library coverage.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0bc43122ad4f0b7f016a3eca63034c8194be7b05b32e324096\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1755, "output": 796, "cacheRead": 23552, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 26103, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782499930642, "responseId": "resp_0bc43122ad4f0b7f016a3eca5b152c8194a54cb51fed07b082"}, "toolResults": []}
